creator: Just-Eat Holding Limited
descriptionHtml:
Partner Centre is your dedicated business management tool that allows you to control many aspects of your online business. You can manage your restaurant's online presence, check invoices, stock up at the JUST EAT Shop and find loads more handy bits and bobs. All in just a few taps on the screen.

Having a problem? Got a suggestion? Simply drop us a line at partner@just-eat.co.uk to let us know and we'll be happy to assist.

descriptionHtml:
The ultimate restaurant convenience app!

Partner Centre is your dedicated business management tool that allows you to control your restaurant's online presence. Review your orders and invoices as they come in, and manage your online settings right from the app!

We're constantly adding new features to make managing your restaurant even easier! If you have a suggestion (or a problem), drop us a line at info@just-eat.co.uk to let us know and we'll be happy to assist.
descriptionShort: Manage your restaurant, wherever you are!
